@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_gnanne(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.abs((v0 + 0.06 / v1 + 0.55)))
    v2 = (wp.abs(wp.sin(v1 + 0.56)) / wp.abs(wp.exp(v0 + 0.45)))
    tmp = 0.64
    v0 = wp.cos((wp.sin(tmp + 0.34) * tmp))
    data[tid] = v0
